| `src/services/order-service.ts` | **CREATE** -- 4 exported functions |
| `src/routes/products.ts` | **MODIFY** -- Thin wrappers calling service |
| `src/routes/orders.ts` | **MODIFY** -- Thin wrappers calling service |
| `src/app.ts` | No change |
| `src/data.ts` | No change |
| `tests/*` | No change |

